John D. NAGLE, as Commissioner of Immigration for the Port of San Francisco, California, Appellant, v. WONG DOO GOW, Appellee. No. 6359. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 8, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and ST. SURE, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
